{"tid":1519540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日唔撚係end game 今晚個餐都唔撚係最後晚餐呀！","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:59:50.000Z","uid":67118,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"44fa2f6c70682c14ad19eefc4db3b0c7d2897df3","tid":1519540,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"我屌 邊個吹風話聽日要end game架 如果聽日end左就真係俾政府過到關<br />\n<br />\n聽日要人人人人人人同人呀<br />\n但係！ 聽日如果去到西環附近 跟返上次818 一定好撚重狗 衝支聯=送頭 <br />\n咁係咪代表勇武唔出嚟？ 又唔係 可以係各區搞狗屋<br />\n將抗爭帶入社區 重點係俾班藍絲試下俾狗咬 食下毒煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地呢個月要嘅目標有兩個！<br />\n1 唔好俾抗爭降溫<br />\n2 等美佬復會<br />\n依家係皇帝唔急太監急 但我地係皇帝個邊<br />\n愈近1/10佢地就會愈急 一急就會出更多嘅錯 可以俾我地放大 同時可以俾更多手牌美國🇺🇸"},{"pid":"e3c334f0f2c3fb76458540f8e7d11fbd3b7a860e","tid":1519540,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d06beebd1096a4a1aba6519582058c06e7a2ff86","tid":1519540,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9103e1941ca9d1bbc8fd66d1a4ddabff6965b","tid":1519540,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3